data.description: REDUCED and NEW PICTURES This is a must see !!  Charming 4-Bedroom Gem - A One-of-a-Kind Opportunity! ??  Are you searching for a special place to call home? Look no further! This delightful 4-bedroom residence is a hidden treasure waiting for someone to infuse it with love and personality.  Key Features:  4 Bedrooms: Plenty of room for your family or guests, each with its own unique charm.  Nearby Schools: Located in the heart of a community served by a top-rated high school and college, ensuring quality education for your family.   Minutes to Downtown: Embrace the vibrant energy of downtown living just moments away, with shopping, dining, and entertainment options aplenty.   Unique Character: This home boasts one-of-a-kind features waiting to be restored and celebrated.  Outdoor Space: Enjoy a spacious yard, perfect for gardening, outdoor activities, or even adding your own touches.  What Makes It Special:   TLC Potential: With a little love and creativity, this home can become a masterpiece reflecting your personal style.   Investment Opportunity: Unlock the full potential of this property and potentially increase its value with the right improvements.   Location, Location, Location: The ideal location near schools and downtown makes this home an incredible find.
